description: Parameter descriptors for transcript access tools

parameters.description: The key development ID for the earnings call transcript. Must be obtained from earnings tools first (get_earnings_from_identifiers, get_latest_earnings_from_identifiers, or get_next_earnings_from_identifiers).
common_mistakes: Using company identifier instead of key_dev_id
Using ticker symbol instead of key_dev_id
Not obtaining key_dev_id from earnings tools first
Guessing key_dev_id values instead of looking them up
Using string format instead of integer for key_dev_id
Expecting this to work without a valid key_dev_id
